sentence: Does EECS 280 have class on Friday ?
sentence-with-vars: Does department0 number0 have class on Friday ?
sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.FRIDAY FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
